overview.en: Times is a block chain supply chain management. It uses the innovative ideas of

to build an ecological platform of supply chain entity business alliance. It mainly provides value-added supply chain management services for global enterprises, and combines block chain with big data to carry out traceable quality management and customer data for upstream and downstream supply chain. Analysis and customization of services and marketing, so that the value of customer resources can be effectively transformed.
overview.zh: Times是区块链供应链管理，其利用“区块链”和“供应链”创新理念打造供应链实体商业联盟生态平台，主要为全球企业提供增值的供应链管理服务，并将区块链和大数据相结合，对供应链上下游进行溯源品质管理、客户数据分析和定制化服务及营销，让客户资源价值有效转化。
